import { Box, Grid, TextField, Typography } from '@mui/material'; import React from 'react' import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom' import Table from '@mui/material/Table'; import TableBody from '@mui/material/TableBody'; import TableCell from '@mui/material/TableCell'; import TableContainer from '@mui/material/TableContainer'; import TableHead from '@mui/material/TableHead'; import TableRow from '@mui/material/TableRow'; import Paper from '@mui/material/Paper'; import { useEffect } from "react"; import { toast } from 'react-toastify'; import 'react-toastify/dist/ReactToastify.css'; export default function OrderDetails() { const {id} = useParams(); const get = async () => { try { let response = await axios.get ( `http://localhost:1337/api/products?filters[category][title][$eq]=${checkedCategory[0]}&filters[category][title][$eq]=${checkedCategory[1]}&filters[category][title][$eq]=${checkedCategory[2]}&filters[category][title][$eq]=${checkedCategory[3]}&filters[category][title][$eq]=${checkedCategory[4]}&populate=*`, { headers: { Authorization: `Bearer ${TOKEN}` } } ); setCategorizeProduct(response.data.data) console.log(response.data.data) } catch(error){ setError(error.message) console.log(error.message) } } useEffect(()=>{ getData(); },[]) return ( {/* */} Order Details ID: $100 Order Date: - Total Amount: - Customer ID: - Order Status: pending {/* */} Shipping Details ID: $100 Full Name: - Email: - Phone: - Delivery Address: pending ID Image Product Category Quantity Subtotal id {/* */} product title categoryName quantity $subtotal {/* */} Subtotal: $
{/* */} ) }
